<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Device Login Detected - DentalKit</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #0f172a; background: #f8fafc; margin: 0; padding: 24px; }
      .container { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(2,6,23,0.06); }
      .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9, #0369a1); color: #ffffff; padding: 28px 28px; text-align: center; }
      .content { padding: 28px; }
      .muted { color: #64748b; font-size: 14px; }
      .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #64748b; font-size: 12px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body role="main">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1 style="margin:0; font-size:24px;">New device login</h1>
        <p style="margin:8px 0 0; opacity:.95;">We detected a sign-in from a new device</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi {{email}},</p>
        <p>A login to your DentalKit account was detected from a new device or location:</p>
        <ul aria-label="Login details">
          <li><strong>Device:</strong> {{userAgent}}</li>
          <li><strong>IP Address:</strong> {{ip}}</li>
          <li><strong>Date/Time:</strong> {{date}}</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="muted">If this was you, no further action is required. If not, please reset your password immediately and contact support.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; {{year}} DentalKit. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html> 